Package: RbowtieCuda
Type: Package
Title: An R Wrapper for nvBowtie and nvBWT, a rewritten version of Bowtie2 for cuda
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2024-12-01
Authors@R: 
        c(person(given = "Jacopo", family = "Pantaleoni", role = c("aut"), 
